{"tid":206911,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"[求救]係車公廟拜完太歲,帶個兩粒糖番屋企食,但最後唔見左","createTime":"2017-04-18T15:44:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-18T18:42:45.000Z","uid":24061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"87dedd81e482e9493d70745b1e066a266c06212d","tid":206911,"uid":24061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T15:44:01.000Z","msg":"話說最近真係行衰運,之前疑似撞到個味野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ,健康一直都好差,病左成個三個幾月都依家都唔好,<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 工作又唔太順利,想話去車公廟轉下運,起碼唔好再病落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ,咁我生肖咁岩就犯太歲,咁就做個拜太歲啦,咁就要帶兩粒糖番去食既拜完太歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ,我就放左係櫃度冇食住<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ,咁今日想話食番個兩粒糖啦,發現唔見左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ,明明好地地放係櫃竟然唔見左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ,問老母係咪掉左,佢有話冇(但極度懷疑係佢見野冇問過我就掉左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ),我想問巴打我係咪成年都冇運行,同我有冇咩可以補救到可以做既?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b5b62c64fb18e1f35fb77d215b2824e2b5e1902","tid":206911,"uid":41138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T15:48:26.000Z","msg":"飲童子尿"},{"pid":"5d71e354866491f28686c9dde81eefb06aaa56c7","tid":206911,"uid":24061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T15:49:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>飲童子尿</blockquote><br />\n 認真呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"895c1adea72ca94a52d07747dd8eb91f3881011b","tid":206911,"uid":6181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T16:01:14.000Z","msg":"咁大個人就唔好咁迷信啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5fff838d6290ccf15